cs.AR, cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper deals with evaluating the vulnerability of feature maps in CNNs in the presence of hardware errors, which falls under the domain of computer architecture (cs.AR) and computer systems and networking (cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a statistical approach to estimate vulnerability, which is related to machine learning (cs.NE).
